author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
The headlines that followed Neil Young's appearance at Glastonbury led me to think about what the festival represents in 2025. Some of those online headlines & comments were savage, but the last person who would care is Neil Young and that's one of the things that makes him great.  

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The latest Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" is here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

title: Has Glastonbury Become A TV Variety Show?
